https://fortran-lang.discourse.group/t/module-dependencies-in-cmake-not-tracked-after-a-module-is-updated/4202/3

===== Install fpm
brew tap fortran-lang/homebrew-fortran
brew install fpm

===== Using fpm
 1091  fpm build
once the toml file is there, things work
 1093  fpm run
 1096  cd src
 1098  vi foo.f90
make one change and everything has to be recompiled
 1100  fpm run


